@plan_support

Our support of the WTB plan alienates the remaining few Marxists in our party, and faces both opposition and support from a variety of sources across the spectrum. Liberals argue that the plan is flawed because it leaves capitalism intact, while some bourgeois bootlickers are cautiously optimistic.

Thankfully, we have not yet convinced the party to formally adopt the plan. Perhaps it is not too late to do the correct thing instead.

