@support_left_progress

We half-heartedly attempt to convince the party to support a program of mass nationalizations in response to the economic crisis. Our few remaining Marxists argue that this policy is in accordance with our long-standing socialist platform, while the pro-bourgeois backstabbers argue that the plan is unrealistic, and that the workers should be grateful for whatever scraps their masters deign to throw them.

We have not yet formally adopted the plan. By the time we will, it may be too late.

